    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>HTML Text Formatting Tags</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        section {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        code {
            background: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 3px 6px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>HTML Text Formatting Tags</h1>
    <p>This page demonstrates commonly used HTML text formatting tags with examples.</p>

    <section>
        <h2>Bold & Strong</h2>
        <p><b>&lt;b&gt;</b> → <b>Bold text</b></p>
        <p><strong>&lt;strong&gt;</strong> → <strong>Strong importance</strong></p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Italic & Emphasis</h2>
        <p><i>&lt;i&gt;</i> → <i>Italic text</i></p>
        <p><em>&lt;em&gt;</em> → <em>Emphasized text</em></p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Underline & Highlight</h2>
        <p><u>&lt;u&gt;</u> → <u>Underlined text</u></p>
        <p><mark>&lt;mark&gt;</mark> → <mark>Highlighted text</mark></p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Small & Deleted Text</h2>
        <p><small>&lt;small&gt;</small> → <small>Smaller text</small></p>
        <p><del>&lt;del&gt;</del> → <del>Deleted text</del></p>
        <p><ins>&lt;ins&gt;</ins> → <ins>Inserted text</ins></p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Subscript & Superscript</h2>
        <p>H<sub>&lt;sub&gt;2</sub>O</p>
        <p>X<sup>&lt;sup&gt;2</sup></p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Code & Preformatted Text</h2>
        <p><code>&lt;code&gt;</code> → <code>printf("Hello World");</code></p>
        <pre>
&lt;pre&gt;
This is
preformatted
text
&lt;/pre&gt;
        </pre>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Keyboard, Sample & Variable</h2>
        <p><kbd>&lt;kbd&gt;</kbd> → <kbd>Ctrl + C</kbd></p>
        <p><samp>&lt;samp&gt;</samp> → <samp>Error 404</samp></p>
        <p><var>&lt;var&gt;</var> → <var>x</var> = 10</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Quotes & Citations</h2>
        <p><q>&lt;q&gt;</q> → <q>Short inline quotation</q></p>
        <blockquote>
            &lt;blockquote&gt; → This is a block quotation.
        </blockquote>
        <p><cite>&lt;cite&gt;</cite> → <cite>HTML Reference</cite></p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Abbreviation</h2>
        <p>
            <abbr title="HyperText Markup Language">&lt;abbr&gt; HTML</abbr>
        </p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Line Break & Horizontal Rule</h2>
        <p>Line one<br>&lt;br&gt;<br>Line two</p>
        <hr>
        <p>&lt;hr&gt; creates a horizontal line above</p>
    </section>

</body>
</html>
